    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Cricket</h2>
        <p>Cricket is a bat-and-ball game played between two teams of 11 players each. It originated in England and is now popular worldwide, especially in countries like India, Australia, South Africa, and England.</p>
        <p>The game is played in various formats, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Test Cricket</strong>: The traditional format played over 5 days.</li>
            <li><strong>One Day Internationals (ODIs)</strong>: A 50-over format.</li>
            <li><strong>T20 Internationals</strong>: A fast-paced 20-over format.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

